Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:04.96,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}As times{\rHonorifics - Narration Off} chan{\r}ge,\Ndifficult cases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:07.00,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's stage is a karaoke box!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.47,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Love and farewell songs during Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:11.17,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:13.34,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.43,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
