Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:18.82,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Producers\NMichihiko Suwa\N(Yomiuri TV)\NMasahito Yoshioka\N(Tokyo Movie)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:42.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I stuck with you guys\Nduring Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:45.23,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:47.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what's up with Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:50.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He only calls once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:54.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his problem?!\NChristmas only comes once a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:56.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a conceited mystery geek!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:58.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:02.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always arrogant,\Nsnobbish, and mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:07.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe that's what I like about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:09.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:12.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? Is there anyone you like, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:15.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there is. Tatsuya Kimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:23.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the guy from Lex,\Nthat rock band! Ta-tsu-ya Ki-mu-ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, just some entertainer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:32.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad got me invited to\None of their live performances!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:35.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to see Tatsuya in the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:35.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to meet them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:40.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's the Suzuki Group's connections for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, I'm totally going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:51.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}chissaku kanjiru don'na toki demo\N...feel so small, any time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:57.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:01.80,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya Kimura (21)\NVocals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Much better than some bands out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya! You've had too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you have\Na talk show after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shove it, ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's totally plastered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:19.86,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Katsumi Yamada (21)\NDrums
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Tatsuya, that's no way to talk to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mari's just doing her job as manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:29.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And have {\i1}you{\i0} been doing\Nyour job as our drummer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Mieko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:36.13,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Mieko Shibazaki (20)\NGuitar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with you today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of your sucky playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:41.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Been waiting for you, Sumii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had my manager reserve this for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:48.14,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Go Sumii (28)\NKaraoke Box Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:48.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I always\Nappreciate your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:51.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That said, it's sad that a former band leader
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is stuck running a joint like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:58.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Don't make me take this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:58.55,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Former band leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:03.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I requested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, Ms. Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:13.33,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Mari Terahara (23)\NManager
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect for you: you {\i1}did{\i0} believe in Santa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:20.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you agree, Ms. Snooty Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:26.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll sing your song.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:29.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:33.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}kurai yomichi wa\NThen one foggy Christmas Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:37.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}pika-pika no...\NSanta came to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}omae no hana ga\NRudolph, with your nose so bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}yaku ni tatsu no sa...\Nwon't you guide my sleigh tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn it! What's he up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:47.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's with that sad look?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna sing too, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:55.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:05:03.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}hoshi no kazu kazoete\NWhen I count the stars in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:12.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}wakatta koto sore wa\NI realized that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:28.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}yasashii hito ni wa hoshi no ai\Nkind people get help from the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:05.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why's that lady crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:11.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To both Mieko and the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quitting Lex?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:18.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm leaving\Nwhen this tour's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:22.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the band knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:26.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good riddance to that hopeless drummer, that bratty guitar player,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:30.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and that snooty manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:41.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's my song!\NWho requested it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya, it's time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to miss the talk show!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:50.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'll sing whenever I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:51.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call the studio to tell them we'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:06:00.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! Bloody Venus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:04.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}ikashita yatsu da ze\NShe's one hot babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:07.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}omae no koto sa\NI'm talkin' about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:15.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}Ah, soba ni ite okure Oh Bloody Venus\NAh, stay by me, oh bloody venus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:24.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}ushinaitakunai no sa omae e no ai\NI don't wanna lose the love I have for you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.79,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tatsuya Kimura passionately{\rHonorifics - Narration Off} san{\r}g
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:08.08,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}his hit song, "Bloody Venus."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:12.01,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Nobody knew his voice
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:15.76,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}would never be heard again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:20.47,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Nobody... except his killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:26.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How was my song?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Katsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme one of them rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:39.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:40.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:45.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you really quitting Lex?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:49.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, my solo debut's coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:50.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Solo debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My new song's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:55.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His new song's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The title? It's called...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:07.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:20.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get an ambulance... Hurry, go get an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:20.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:28.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's no good! He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That smells like cyanide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:33.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Somebody planned this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:37.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who could've done this, right in front of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:43.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The first suspect was Sumii,\Nthe guy who brought the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:47.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He and Tatsuya Kimura\Nused to be bandmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:51.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But then Tatsuya went pro\Nand became popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:54.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It looked like a jealousy murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:58.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But he was cleared of suspicion\Nwhen we learned
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}that everyone had eaten the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:07.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Furthermore, toxins were found on the\Nvictim's clothes and microphone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:10.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}so he had touched the poison\Nbefore eating the rice ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:14.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, the killer placed poison on the microphone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:20.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,which indirectly adhered\Nto him when he grabbed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:24.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means it was done by\Nthe person who{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}g before him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:27.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...you, Mieko Shibazaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:33.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}g a\Nfarewell song while crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:37.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:43.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya didn't dump me!\NHe turned me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mieko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:48.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I told him how I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:51.91,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Sorry, Mieko. I already have someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.42,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She's gone right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:59.59,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but I'm waiting for her to come back. And she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:02.22,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:07.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said it couldn't work out between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then to pay him back, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:13.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I didn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Someone he liked...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:19.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector. It was Tatsuya who requested\Nthe song that she{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}g!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:23.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She had no idea that\Nhe'd be singing next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:27.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she couldn't have\Npoisoned the microphone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}is{\i0} true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:34.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, who requested\Nhis Bloody Venus song?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:45.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} always take\Nhis jacket off when he{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}g?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only at the start of every Bloody Venus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:56.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! What part of his clothing\Nhad cyanide on it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:10:00.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His left elbow area, I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On his staff jacket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:06.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there was nothing on his jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:10.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's it! Now I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:13.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}how the killer poisoned Tatsuya Kimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:20.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And that killer is one of those three\Nwho have the same jacket on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guitar lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:31.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The manager and Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwere arguing earlier;
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:34.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,were they always like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:38.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They argued about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:41.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya always started it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not as bad as he claimed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:48.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's smart, serious, and beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:50.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And she never caused any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:53.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:56.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We found these in Tatsuya Kimura's locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:11:01.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything useful here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:06.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture... A band picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:11.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's from when he and I had a band
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:14.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,before he went pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:17.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But only he and this person are still
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:20.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in the music industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:24.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't the only one who left your band?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:27.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:31.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya said that person's why he wanted to quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that person's not in that picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:39.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ged, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much, if you ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's something written on the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:12:00.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But what a sad incident\Nthis is if it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:09.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who did it? How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. Okay. Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:17.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancel the investigation!\NGet everyone back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:24.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"He?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:26.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A great detective you know very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:30.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:38.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Shin'ichi came back. He finally came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:49.03,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Welcome! Thank you all for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:55.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi Kudo must be watching with this camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Shin'ichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:02.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin unraveling this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:07.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, what's with this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.30,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:13.22,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's a Christmas song, it's played everywhere during Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:18.60,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It also stirred up the\Nkiller's hatred for the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:23.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the killer is the one who Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} requested this song for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.15,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yes. Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio}-san{\r}'s killer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:29.45,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}was his manager,\NMari Terahara{\rHonorifics - Radio}-san{\r}! It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}manager{\i0} killed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:38.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop kidding around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:42.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't even in\Nthe room when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:47.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've poisoned him\Ndespite your distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,simply by having him\Nsing this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:55.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was his hit song,\N"Bloody Venus!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:02.65,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Well, could you sing for us,\Nusing the mic I've prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.19,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's no poison on it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:11.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll sing, if that'll make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:18.50,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Please wait! Why aren't you\Nremoving your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:23.71,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio}-san{\r} always took his jacket off when he{\rHonorifics - Radio} san{\r}g this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.50,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Isn't that right, people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.64,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't forget the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:44.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}ikashita yatsu da ze\NShe's one hot babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:47.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}omae no koto sa\NI'm talkin' about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:55.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}Ah, soba ni ite okure Oh Bloody Venus\NAh, stay by me, oh bloody venus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:15:02.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}ushinaitakunai no sa omae e no ai\NI don't wanna lose the love I have for you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}Ah, kanjite okure\NAh, feel it with me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22}I love ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! She's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:58.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She used to sing with\NTatsuya in my band.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The manager...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.93,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:19.89,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now try eating\Nthe food I've prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:20.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.27,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just as Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio}-san{\r} did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.69,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Pick whatever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:29.28,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Assuming you can, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:36.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not. I touched him\Nafter he collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:40.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His hands and clothes\Nhad poison on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:43.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could've gotten\Nsome on my hands then, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:48.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please check\Nher jacket, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:50.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:56.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for the jacket!\NI put it on after touching Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there {\i1}is{\i0} poison on it,\Nthat doesn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:03.93,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No. It's not poison\NI'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:09.44,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s missing lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:18.16,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}In other words,\Nthat's not her jacket:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:22.79,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}she switched hers with Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio}-san{\r}'s\Nto dispose of the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:28.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She wiped poison on the\Ninside of the left elbow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:34.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so that some of it would\Nget on his shirt underneath
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:37.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when he put the jacket on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:41.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All that remained was\Nto have him sing Bloody Venus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:45.98,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}During his dance,\Nhe threw the jacket off
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.94,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and touched his left elbow with his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:55.86,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Afterward, he died of poisoning\Nwhen he ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:01.70,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Her motive is in the\Nphotograph on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:06.66,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's from when Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio}-san{\r} was\Nin Sumii{\rHonorifics - Radio}-san{\r}'s band.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:13.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one else in the picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:17.09,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She {\i0}is{\i1} there, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:21.05,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}In the center of the picture,\Nwith Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:25.64,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's right. That picture\Nof her is the very motive
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.48,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}behind this murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:32.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I had plastic surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:40.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love with him back then, when we were on the band...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So when he went pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:48.12,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Come with me, Mari!\NYou can be my manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:51.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy when he said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he felt\Nthe same way about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:58.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I got the surgery\Nto be worthy of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:02.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But his attitude suddenly\Nchanged after I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd constantly call me ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:08.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He even had me sing\Nthe Rudolph song earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:12.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} why he requested\Nthe song for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:16.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He made me his manager\Njust to insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:19.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I couldn't forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:20.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I loved him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:25.43,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You're wrong, Mari{\rHonorifics - Radio}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:30.58,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Tatsuya{\rHonorifics - Radio}-san{\r} had been in love\Nwith you for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:33.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense! What would you know about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:36.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mari! He's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector. Can I have that photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:44.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a love song he wrote about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:47.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"I want to talk with the real you"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:55.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were the lyrics\Nto his newest song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:58.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He always talked about you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:00.61,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why's Mari so self-conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:04.03,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why'd she{\rHonorifics - Flashback} chan{\r}ge her face for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:07.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he always treated me like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:11.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't good at expressing himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:14.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he wanted the old you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:29.18,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm waiting for her to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:35.19,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Sorry, Mieko. I already have someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:39.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The girl he liked was the manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:43.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya! Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:57.00,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The combination of a man unable to express his feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:03.47,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and a woman who hid hers, brought forth a sad ending
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.68,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}in her weeping and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:11.77,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Only her photograph sadly smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:52.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. That's what you get for\Nusing the name "Shin'ichi Kudo..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:54.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been waiting there 3 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.55,0:21:56.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for you to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:02.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could help,\Nbut there's nothing I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:08.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:16.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi? Are you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:18.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi? Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:22.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Say something\Nif you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:26.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:27.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:31.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:36.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:39.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:41.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:43.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:46.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.27,0:22:49.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you {\i1}that{\i0} desperate to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:50.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.81,0:22:53.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see you, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:58.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:22:59.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wish you could see\Nyourself right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.82,0:23:02.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.58,0:23:06.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, gotta get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.12,0:23:10.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still haven't finished that case.\NLater, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:12.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:15.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:22.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(1000,0)}"Your Christmas present.\NHope you like it! — Shin'ichi"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:30.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Now stop worrying about me, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:47.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:50.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...your mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.10,0:23:51.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:54.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Conan Edogawa doesn't have a mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:56.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Agasa—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:05.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who's that masked guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:08.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:14.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.57,0:24:19.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Night Baron
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.84,0:24:21.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Merry Christmas! And have a good year!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This coming year's gonna be interesting!
